  ============================================================
  HOW THIS FILE IS ORGANIZED (read this first!)
  ============================================================
  This is ONE file with everything in it: HTML, CSS, and JS.
  Scroll down and you'll find clearly labeled sections:

    1. FONTS & COLORS   -> change the look of the whole site here
    2. HEADER / NAV      -> the terminal-style menu at the top
    3. ABOUT ME
    4. SKILLS            (optional — delete the whole <section> if you don't want it)
    5. PROJECTS          -> duplicate one <article class="card"> to add a new project
    6. CERTIFICATES      -> duplicate one <article class="cert"> to add a new certificate
    7. CONTACT           (kept last, as requested)
    8. SCRIPT            -> small bit of JS, you usually won't need to touch this

  Every section has comments like this one. Look for "EDIT:" —
  that marks the exact spot you'll usually want to change.
  ============================================================
